e obsessive and increasingly narcissistic. Achieving Inner Balance in Anxious Times shows us how to become aware of the darker side of our personalities, and how to avoid conflict and power struggles by establishing clear ego boundaries that help build mutual trust and respect in our personal and professional lives. The achievement of inner balance makes work-life balance possible.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 0aBehavior modification. 0aPeace of mind. 7aSELF-HELP / General.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978077358552240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780773585522423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780773585522/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles